Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完二君的事件后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者皆为女性这一共同点就不存在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们看漏了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此  但还有什么共同点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么都行  再多搜集些情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  我妈好像说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生田目议员辞职后回到这个城里继承了家业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在是快递员对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山野女主播的婚外情对象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他自然是没法继续当议员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那家伙有不在场证明对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像和犯人没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有没有其他的线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山野女主播在案发前因为婚外情的报道上了新闻对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西学姐也作为第一目击证人上了新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等等  记得天城确实也接受过电视台的采访吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二同学也在特别节目里出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽说我根本不愿意回想起那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说所有人在消失前都上过电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与电视有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么被电视报道的人就会成为犯人的下一个目标？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是究竟是谁  又是出于什么目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于犯人的动机我们依然一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一个劲地聊天  给我好好拾垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们今后必须更加关注电视了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能浏览各种节目来提防犯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令营之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是有那种喜好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着这个机会我希望你实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的贞操正面临着危机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了我不是那种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的反应为什么这么激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更让人觉得你真的是那种人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在已经能接受女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说  我们还是很难相信你…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在你的身边很需要勇气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  你不是已经接受我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就到女生的帐篷里走一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们看看我的男子汉气概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看了我巽完二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被诸金知道了可是会被停学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鼻子和嘴堵上的话就能让她停止打呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你可千万别这么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Per熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你们来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们回不了帐篷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  完二君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然闯了进来然后就晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下我们没法入睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则起来之后恐怕会引发骚乱对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这里有没有坏学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了  是诸金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先藏在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}把你们全都停学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你靠得太近了啊花村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们已经睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  在的话就给我出个声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  给我闭上嘴好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  好像有点喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己一下子老了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们准备怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总  总之现在没法出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会在明早别人起床前出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  没什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别越过这条界啊  男生们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这也太挤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做什么奇怪的事啊  花村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们度过了一个充满各种窘迫事件的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perosna
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}6月18日  星期六  天气  「多云转晴」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令营第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就结束了啊  夏令营
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  谁也没有被停学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  好不容易来了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先来游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你要游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我浑身酸痛就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天晚上睡得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有和任何人一起睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你们别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个人游泳的话也太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个去游不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你们好像还欠我们一个人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情是欠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我们没带泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  嗯  真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUNES自有品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是初夏的新款式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你买东西时所说的急事就是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你真是太有才了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  她们到哪去换衣服了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  你的这条泳裤真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很时髦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真时髦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么直勾勾地盯着人家看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一声不吭  快说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的泳衣都很般配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲至极
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是超乎想象的棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说内容还是有点孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们将来一定会成长为好女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  鸣上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…  完二君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于要把人踹下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓吧  反正你们都是要下去的对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸金？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝多了  真难受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  好像顺着水流过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我臭不臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又失去了某些重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  幸好我们还没进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:21:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我喜欢的类型  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你忘了昨天晚上的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他一个人待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:09.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c000000}人之间的羁绊就是真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  哥哥
Comment: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.14,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}下条线索
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定会被绑架对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.83,0:24:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是犯人的犯罪预告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.90,0:24:31.45,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}下集  真正的我无人知晓
